    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but you said it's \"inherently dangerous\"... isn't that a bit of a stretch? like, surely there's a version of it that's actually good and not just about hating other people. can you explain why you're leaning towards it being dangerous rather than just a normal way for people to feel connected to their country?",
