    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty strong take. it sounds like you're saying any form of national pride is basically just a stepping stone to being intolerant. if that's the case, are you basically saying that the only healthy way for a society to function is to move past nationalism entirely and focus on globalism instead?",
